name: Exhibition Poster "Kapan Pun dan Dimanapun"
description:
Exhibition Poster "Anytime and Anywhere"
My first solo exhibition poster to respond to art boredom. I became an artist and curator there.
The exhibition is a series of the 8th East Java Biennale.

Poster Pameran "Kapan Pun dan Dimanapun"
Poster pameran tunggal pertama saya untuk merespon kebosanan akan seni. Saya menjadi seniman sekaligus kurator disana. 
Pameran adalah serangkaian dari Biennale Jawa Timur ke 8.
